quran[27{c,v,t}:
83,35,masnadon par baithy hue un ka haal dekh rahay hain
83,36,mil gaya na kafiroon ko unn harkato ka sawab jo woh kya karte thay
84,1,jab aasman phatt jaye ga
84,2,aur apne Rab ke farmaan ki tameel kere ga aur uss ke liye haq yahi hai ( ke apne Rab ka hukum manay )
84,3,aur jab zameen phela di jaye gi
84,4,aur jo kuch is ke andar hai ussay bahar pheink kar khaali ho jaye gi
84,5,aur apne Rab ke hukum ki tameel kere gi aur uss ke liye haq yahi hai ( ke is ki tameel kere )
84,6,"ae ensaan, to kushan kushan apne Rab ki taraf chala ja raha hai, aur uss se milnay wala hai"
84,7,phir jis ka nama aamaal uss ke seedhay haath mein diya gaya
84,8,uss se halka hisaab liya jaye ga
84,9,aur woh apne logon ki taraf khush khush palty ga
84,10,raha woh shakhs jis ka nama aamaal uss ki peeth ke peechay diya jaye ga
84,11,to woh mout ko pukare ga
84,12,aur bharakti hui aag mein ja parre ga
84,13,woh apne ghar walon mein magan tha
84,14,uss ne samgha tha ke usay kabhi palatna nahi hai
84,15,"palatna kaisay nah tha, uss ka Rab uss ke kartoot dekh raha tha"
84,16,"pas nahi, mein qasam khata hon shafaq ki"
84,17,aur raat ki aur jo kuch woh samaitt layte hai
84,18,aur chaand ki jab ke woh mah kaamil ho jata hai
84,19,tum ko zaroor darja badarja aik haalat se doosri haalat ki taraf guzarte chalay jana hai
84,20,phir inn logon ko kya ho gaya hai ke yeh imaan nahi laatay
84,21,aur jab quran inn ke samnay parha jata hai to sajda nahi karte ?
84,22,balkay yeh munkareen to ulta jutlatay hain
84,23,halaank jo kuch yeh ( apne nama aamaal mein ) jama kar rahay hain Allah ussay khoob jaanta hai
84,24,lehaza inn ko dard naak azaab ki basharat day do
84,25,Albata jo log imaan le aeye hain aur jinhon ne naik amal kiye hain un ke liye kabhi khatam nah honay wala ajar hai
